user.biography: 💨 Because life's too short to smoke bad cigars 💨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cigar Aficionado in Los Angeles, California with @ashcigarlounge. May be an image of living room.

node.text:
The @ashcigarlounge in Los Angeles, California is a work- and cigar-friendly environment that also features this Illuminati Lounge for private gatherings. Link in bio for more pictures.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife #wheretosmoke #california #LA #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cigar Aficionado in Estelí with @j.c.newmancigarco. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text:
The Yaguas are back. Introduced by @j.c.newmancigarco last year, Yagua is made using palm leaves to create the shape of a cigar, rather than molds or presses like nearly all handmade cigars on sale today. It's an old tradition from 1940s Cuba. Link in bio for more details.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife #yagua #nicaragua #nicaraguancigars

node.text:
#CigaroftheWeek Perla Del Mar Corojo Robusto from @j.c.newmancigarco: Evenly box-pressed with subtle edges and a triple cap. Initial wasabi spiciness settles down for a warm smoke of dark-roasted Ethiopian coffee, dried fruit, wood and a tangy citrus finish.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife #nicaragua #nicaraguancigars

node.text:
#CigaroftheWeek Oliva Serie G Maduro Presidente by @olivacigar: Quite large and box-pressed, this cigar has an even burn and open draw that delivers a robust smoke of coffee and licorice with some secondary notes of spice, cocoa and toast.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife #nicaragua #nicaraguancigars #oliva

node.text:
#CigaroftheWeek Trinidad Media Luna from @habanos_oficial: There’s slight resistance on the draw of this pigtailed robusto, which burns slow and cool. Every puff exhibits a clear flavor trio of salt, wood and fruit with floral, herbal undertones. An interesting smoke.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Cigar Aficionado on August 16, 2021 tagging @aganorsaleaf.

node.text:
@AganorsaLeaf's new Supreme Leaf Torpedo should be reaching retailers now. The 6-inch-by-54-ring Torpedo is made with the same Nicaraguan blend as the rest of the brand, which showcases a Corojo ’99 wrapper. Link in bio for more details.⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
⁠
#cigar #cigars #cigaraficionado #cigaraficionadomagazine #thegoodlife #nicaragua #nicaraguancigars
